Definition: a terrorist group formed in the 1980s in Sierra Leone
Example: seeks to overthrow the government and gain control of the diamond producing regions; responsible for attacks on civilians and children, widespread torture and murder and using children to commit atrocities; sponsored by the president of Liberia
Synonyms: RUF, terrorist_organization, i, noun, act, terrorism, c, location, Sierra_Leone, r, a, terrorist, group, formed, in, the, s, Sierra, Leone, seeks, to, overthrow, government, and, gain, control, of, diamond, producing, regions, responsible, for, attacks, on, civilians, children, widespread, torture, murder, using, commit, atrocities, sponsored, by, president, Liberia
Category: noun.group
